tafsir[64]{c,v,t}:
  24,1,"Ndee ko Simoore Men Tellinii nde, Men wajimmbini gollirgol ﾃ疎awooje mayre, Men Tellini e mayre Aayeeje ﾉ殿nnguﾉ容; joortagol wonnde on waajitorta ko woni kon e nder mayre immorde e ﾃ疎awooje ﾉ容n koni ngollironnde."
  24,2,"Debbo jeenoowo e gorko jinoowo jiwo e suka piyee gooto kala e maﾉ橡兎 paatawol teemedere, wata newaare e yurmeende nanngu on haa ronkon ﾃｱimnude e maﾉ橡兎 hiddi ndin maaﾉ蓉n newinanon ﾉ兎 ﾉ蓉m, si tawii on laatiki hiﾉ熔n gomﾉ擁ni Alla e ﾃ疎laande Laakara nden, yo tawe ﾃｱimnugol hiddi ndin e maﾉ橡兎 jamaa gomﾉ擁nﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n fii kempinngol lollinngol fii maﾉ橡兎, e haﾉ擁rgol kamﾉ兎 ﾉ擁ﾉ熔 tanaa maﾉ橡兎."
  24,3,"Ka hulﾉ妬nngol fii jeeno Alla jaﾅ逆ii wonnde on gaadariiﾉ熔 ﾉ蓉m o rerﾉ預ntaa fii resugol si wanaa debbo jinoowo wano makko maaﾉ蓉m sirkoowo mo rentotaako e jina wonndude e waasude dagagol resugol mo, on debbo wowtiniiﾉ熔 jeeno o rerﾉ預n- taa reseede si wanaa gorko jinoowo wano makko maaﾉ蓉m sirkoowo mo rentotaako hurum jom galle makko, na harminaa e dow gomﾉ擁nﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n resugol debbo jinoowo on e resinngol gorko jInoowo on."
  24,4,"E ﾉ兎n ﾉ兎 no werloo ko pankare e sonnaaﾉ兎 nantiiﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n, (e worﾉ兎 reeniiﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n wano sonnaa-ﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n non), refti hara ﾉ兎 addaali seedeeﾉ兎 nayo e dow ko ﾉ兎 werlii kon e maﾉ橡兎 immorde e bonki haray piyee ﾉ兎 -an ﾃｱaawoowo on- paatawol cappanﾉ容 jeetati, wata on jaﾉ殿n ﾉ兎 seedeeyaagal poomaa. Ko ﾉ兎n ﾉ熔n woni tukkude nantiiﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n, ko kamﾉ兎 woni yaltuﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n e gaayi doftaare Alla nden."
  24,5,"Si wanaa ﾉ兎n tuubuﾉ兎 ka Alla ﾉ殿awo nden huunde nde ﾉ兎 waﾉ擁 , ﾉ兎 moﾆｴﾆｴintini golle maﾉ橡兎, haray pellet, Alla jaﾉ殿y tuubuubuyee maﾉ橡兎 on e seedeeyaagal maﾉ橡兎 ngal, pellet, Alla ko O Surroowo wonannde on tuubuﾉ熔 immorde e jeyaaﾉ兎 Makko ﾉ兎n, ko O Yurmeteeﾉ熔 ﾉ兎."
  24,6,"E ﾉ兎n worﾉ兎 tukkooﾉ兎 sonnaaﾉ兎 mu'un hara alanaa ﾉ兎 seedeeﾉ兎 tanaa wonkiiji maﾉ橡兎 ﾉ兎 no seedoo e dow sellugol ko ﾉ兎 tukkiri ko [sonnaaﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n]; ko yo gooto [kala] e maﾉ橡兎 seedo seedeeji nayi [o woondira] Alla, pellet kanko, ko o goonguﾉ熔 e ko o tukkiri kon sonnaajo makko on immorde e jina."
  24,7,"Refti e nder seedagol makko jowaﾉ登l ngol o ﾉ兎yda huﾉ擁rgol wonkii makko jojjidugol e kuddi ndin si o laatike fenuﾉ蓉 e ko o tukkire kon [sonnaajo on]."
  24,8,"Sakko [sonnaajo on] jojja sabu ﾉ蓉m hiddeede hiddi jeeno ngon, o martinira e makko ngol hiddegol, nde kanko o seedotoo seedeeji nayi [o woondira] Alla: ""Pellet [gorko on] ko o fenuﾉ熔 e ko o tukkiri mo kon."
  24,9,"Refti e nder seedagol makko jowaﾉ登l ngol o ﾉ兎yda huﾉ擁rgol wonkii makko kin tikkere Alla nden e dow makko si [gorko on] laatike goonguﾉ熔 e nder ko o tukkiri mo kon."
  24,10,"Sinndo wanaano ﾆ「ral Alla ngal e dow mooﾉ熔n -onon yimﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n- e Yurmeende Makko nden e mooﾉ熔n, e wonndema kadi Kank ko O jaﾉ殿noowo tuubuubuyee kala tuubuﾉ熔 immorde e jeyaaﾉ兎 Makko ﾉ兎n, ko O ﾃ粗eﾃｱo ka fewjoore Makko e ka Sari'a Makko O yaccinanayno on Lepte ﾉ容n e dow bakkatuuji mo'on ﾉ擁n, O wirtirayno on sabu majji."
  24,11,"Pellet, ﾉ兎n adduﾉ兎 penaale ﾉ容n (ﾉ蓉m le ko tukkirgol bonki Yumma gomﾉ擁nﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n Aa'isa yo Alla weltor mo) ko ﾉ兎 jamaa dammbitiiﾉ熔(askitiido) e mooﾉ熔n, -onon gomﾉ擁nﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n- wata on sikku ko ﾉ兎 fefindii kon ko bone mo'on, ko woni, ﾉ蓉m ko moﾆｴﾆｴere sabu ko woni kon e mu'un immorde e mbarjaari e ndarndagol gomﾉ擁nﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n, e ko jokki ﾉ蓉m kon e laﾉ橡妬nngol Yumma gomﾉ擁nﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n. No woodani kala tawaaﾉ熔 e tukkirgol [NeenAa'isa] bonki njoﾉ電i ko o faggitii kon immorde e junuubu sabu wowlugol makko ngol penaale ﾉ容n, e on fawtiiﾉ熔 ko mawni kon e ﾉ蓉m sabu fuﾉ遼預gol makko ﾉ蓉m, no woodani mo Lepte mawﾉ容. Ko faandaa e ﾉ蓉m ko hooreejo naafiqiiﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n Abdullaahi bun Ubayyu bun Saluulu."
  24,12,"Ko haanunoo si worﾉ兎 gomﾉ擁nﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n e rewﾉ兎 gomﾉ擁nﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n nanii ﾉ容e penaale mawﾉ容 ﾉ兎 hooloo hisugol on mo ﾉ蓉m fenaa on e hoore-mu'un immorde e musiﾉ橡兎 maﾉ橡兎 gomﾉ擁nﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n, ﾉ兎 wi'a: ""ﾆ隔m ko fenaande ﾉ殿nngunde nii""."
  24,13,"Ko haanunoo ko nde fefindiiﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n e dow Yumma gomﾉ擁nﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n Aa'isa yo Alla weltor mo addaynoo seedeeﾉ兎 nayo e dow ngol fefindagol maﾉ橡兎 mawngol, ﾉ兎 seedoo e dow sellugol ko ﾉ兎 dammbi kon e makko, si tawii ﾉ兎 addaali seedeeﾉ兎 nayo e dow ﾉ蓉m -te ﾉ兎 addataa ﾉ兎 poomaa- haray kamﾉ兎 ko ﾉ兎 fenooﾉ兎 ka ﾃ疎awoore Alla."
  24,14,"Sinndo wonaano ﾆ「ral Alla ngal e dow mooﾉ熔n -onon gomﾉ擁nﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n- e Yurmeende Makko nden e mooﾉ熔n nde tawnoo O yaccinantaa on Lepte ﾉ容n, O laﾉ橡妬ni ﾉ兎n tuubuﾉ兎 immorde e muuﾉ熔n; heﾉ殿yno on Lepte mawﾉ容 sabu ko ukkiﾉ熔n kon e mu'un immorde e fenaande e fefindagol e dow Yumma gomﾉ擁nﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n."
  24,15,"Tuma yoga maﾉ橡兎 fillantoo nde yoga, hiﾉ熔n eggira nde kunnduﾉ容 mooﾉ熔n wonndude e bonugol mayre; alanah on e ﾉ蓉m ganndal, hiﾉ熔n sikka wonnde ﾉ蓉m ko newiiﾉ蓉m, hara le ﾉ蓉m ko mawnuﾉ蓉m ka Alla; sabu ko woni kon e mu'un immorde e fenaande e tukkugol laaﾉ砥ﾉ熔."
  24,16,"Ko haanunoo tuma nanuﾉ熔n ndee fenaande, wi'on: ""Sellantaa men nde men wowlata oo fiyaake kaanuﾉ熔, Senayee wonanii Ma Joomi amen, ndee huunde nde ﾉ兎 werlii ﾉ蓉m e Yumma gomﾉ擁nﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n ko fenaande mawnde""."
  24,17,"Alla no anndintinnde on O laaﾉ殿na on fii wata on fillito yeru ndee fenaande werloﾉ熔n bonki e laaﾉ砥ﾉ熔, si tawii on laatike gomﾉ擁nﾉ兎 Alla."
  24,18,"Alla no ﾉ殿nnginannde on Aayeeje moftuﾉ容 ﾉ容n ﾃ疎awooje Makko ﾉ容n e Waajuuji Makko ﾉ擁n, Alla ko O Annduﾉ熔 golle mon ﾉ容n, hay e huunde suﾉ預naaki e majje, aray O yoﾉ殿 on e dow majje, ko O ﾃ粗eﾃｱo ka Fewjoore Makko e ka Sari'a Makko."
  24,19,"Pellet, ﾉ兎n yiﾉ蓉ﾉ兎 yo pankare ﾉ容 lollu e hoore gomﾉ擁nﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n -no jeyaa e majji tukkirgol jeeno ngon- no woodani ﾉ兎 Lepte muusuﾉ容 ka aduna sabu ﾃｱimnugol hiddi tukkugol e dow maﾉ橡兎, no woodani ﾉ兎 kadi ka Laakara Lepte Yiite, Alla no Anndi penaale maﾉ橡兎 ﾉ容n, e ko fiyakuuji jeyaaﾉ兎 Makko ﾉ兎n wontata, hiMo Anndi kadi nafaaji maﾉ橡兎 ﾉ擁n, onon on anndah ﾉ蓉m."
  24,20,"Sinndo wonaano ﾆ「ral Alla ngal e dow mooﾉ熔n -onon ﾉ兎e ukkiiﾉ兎 e penaale- e Yurmeende Makko nden e mo'on, sinndo wonaano pellet Alla ko O Newiiﾉ熔 Hinnotooﾉ熔 on, O yaccinanayno on Lepte ﾉ容n."
  24,21,"Ko onon yo ﾉ兎n gomﾉ擁nﾉ兎 Alla golliri Sari'a Makko on, wata on jokku ﾉ預te Seytaane ﾉ容n sabu cuﾉ蓉gol makko ngol meere nden, kala jokkuﾉ熔 ﾉ預ti makko ﾉ擁n pellet, o yamiray mo ko kaani kon immorde e konnguﾉ擁 e kuuﾉ容, e ko sari'a on aﾃｱi kon, sinndo wonaano ﾆ「ral Alla ngal e dow mooﾉ熔n -onon gomﾉ擁nﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n- hay e gooto e mo'on laaﾉ妬rtaano tuubuubuyee on poomaa hay o tuubi, kono Alla hiMo laﾉ橡妬nira on mo O Muuyi jaﾉ殿nngol mo tuubuubuyee makko on, Alla ko O Nanoowo konnguﾉ擁 mo'on ﾉ擁n, Annduﾉ熔 golle mo'on ﾉ容n, hay e huunde e majje suuﾉ預naaki Mo, aray O yoﾉ殿 on e dow majje."
  24,22,"Wata jom ﾉ砥ral en ka Diina e jom yaajeende en ka jawdi woondu fii ﾉ預lugol okkugol ﾉ殿dondiraaﾉ兎 maﾉ橡兎 hatonnjinﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n, -sabu ﾉ妬llaare nde ﾉ兎 woni nden e mu'un, immorde e ﾉ兎n feruﾉ兎 ka Laawol Alla- sabu junuubu mo ﾉ兎 waﾉ遼擁tii ﾉ蓉n, yo ﾉ兎 yaafano ﾉ兎, ﾉ兎 yawtanaﾉ兎. Kaa on yiﾉ預h yo Alla yawtan on junubaaji mo'on ﾉ擁n si on yaafanike ﾉ兎 on yawtii?! Alla ko O Surroowo wonannde on tuubuﾉ熔 immorde e jeyaaﾉ兎 Makko ﾉ兎n, ko O Yurmeteeﾉ熔 ﾉ兎, yo jeyaaﾉ兎 Makko ﾉ兎n ﾃｱentin Mo. O Aaya ko fii Abuu Bakri Asiddiiqi (yo Alla weltor mo) ngal Tellii tuma nde o woondunoo fii ﾉ預lugol nafkugol Mistahu sabu tawtugol makko pene ﾉ容n."
  24,23,"ﾆ‘n tukkooﾉ兎 rewﾉ兎 nantiiﾉ兎 welsindiiﾉ兎 e pankare ﾉ兎n, ﾉ兎n ﾉ兎 tawata miijo bonugol aratah e maﾉ橡兎, ﾉ兎 raﾉ預ama e yurmeende Alla nden aduna e laakara. No woodani ﾉ兎 lepte mawnuﾉ容 laakara."
  24,24,"Heﾉ殿y ﾉ兎 ﾉ容n Lepte ﾃ疎lnde Darngal, ﾃ疎lnde seedoytoo e dow maﾉ橡兎 ﾉ容nﾉ容 maﾉ橡兎 ﾉ容n ko ﾉ兎 wowlirnoo ﾉ容 kon immorde e meere, seedoyoo e dow maﾉ橡兎 kadi juuﾉ容 maﾉ橡兎 ﾉ容n e koyﾉ容 maﾉ橡兎 ﾉ容n sabu ko ﾉ兎 laatinoo kon hiﾉ兎 golla."
  24,25,"E nder ngal ﾃ疎llal Alla huuﾉ妬nanay ﾉ兎 njoﾉ電i maﾉ橡兎 ndin e Nunﾉ預l, ﾉ兎 annda kadi pellet, Alla Senayee wonanii Mo ko Kanko woni Goonga, kala ko iwri e Makko immorde e kumpital maaﾉ蓉m fodoore maaﾉ蓉m kammbaa ko Goonga ﾉ殿nnguka sikke alah e makka."
  24,26,"Kala ko soﾉ妬 immorde ka worﾉ兎 e ka rewﾉ兎 e ka konnguﾉ擁 e ka kuuﾉ容 na yaadi ina hawri e kala huunde soﾉ砥nde. Kala ko laaﾉ妬 kon kadi immorde e ﾉ蓉m haray ko dammbondirﾉ蓉m e hawrondirﾉ蓉m e kala huunde laaﾉ砥nde. ﾆ‘n worﾉ兎 laaﾉ砥ﾉ兎 e rewﾉ兎 laaﾉ砥ﾉ兎 ko ﾉ兎 martinaaﾉ兎 e ko worﾉ兎 soﾉ砥ﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n e rewﾉ兎 soﾉ砥ﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n wowlata ﾉ兎 kon. No woodani ﾉ兎 haforaneede immorde ka Alla hiMo haforira ﾉ蓉m bakkatuuji maﾉ橡兎, no woodani ﾉ兎 arsike tedduﾉ熔 ﾉ蓉m le ko Aljanna on."
  24,27,"Ko onon yo gomﾉ擁nﾉ兎 Alla golliri Sari'a Makko on, wata on naatu e cuuﾉ擁 ﾉ擁 wonaa cuuﾉ擁 mo'on haa duﾅ喫noﾉ熔n hoﾉ蓉ﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n e majji fii naatugol tawa ﾉ兎, salminon e maﾉ橡兎, wi'on ka salminngol e ka duﾅ喫nagol: ""Kisiyee e mooﾉ蓉n, yo mi naatu?"" Ko ngol duﾅ喫nagol ngol yamiraﾉ熔n ﾉ蓉m ﾉ砥ri moﾆｴﾆｴannde on diini naatugol juha. Bela jo'o on annditay ko yamiraﾉ熔n kon ﾉ熔ftoﾉ熔n ﾉ蓉m."
  24,28,"Si on tawaali goﾉ遼熔 e nder ﾉ擁n cuuﾉ擁, haray wata on naatu e majji haa duﾅ蟻nee on naatugol e majji immorde e ﾉ兎n jeyﾉ兎 duﾅ蟻yee(sakkitoore) on. Si jeyﾉ兎 ﾉ擁 ﾉ兎n wi'anii on: (Ruttee) haray ruttee wata on naatu e majji, pellet, ko ﾉ蓉m ﾉ砥ri laaﾉ殿nnde on ka Alla, Alla non hiMo Anndi ko golloton hay e huunde e golle mo'on ﾉ容n suuﾉ預naaki Mo, aray O yoﾉ殿 on e dow majje."
  24,29,"Junuubu fawaaki on si on naatii hara on duﾅ喫naaki e cuuﾉ擁 kafaaﾉ擁 ﾉ擁 gooto hertoraa jeyal mu'um, heblanaaﾉ擁 fii ko nafa yimﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n fow; wano birooji ﾉ擁n e bitikaaji ﾉ擁n ka maakitiiji, Alla no Anndi ko feﾃｱﾃｱinton immorde e golle mo'on e alhaaliiji mo'on e ko suuﾉ熔ton, hay huunde e ﾉ蓉m suuﾉ預naaki Mo, aray O yoﾉ殿 on e dow mu'un."
  24,30,"Maakan -an Nulaaﾉ熔- worﾉ兎 gomﾉ擁nﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n yo ﾉ兎 hippu giti maﾉ橡兎 ﾉ容n gaayi ndaarude e ko daganaki ﾉ兎 immorde e sonnaaﾉ兎 e awraaji, ﾉ兎 reena farjuuji maﾉ橡兎 immorde e yanugol e ko harminaa kon, e immorde e huncugol ﾉ蓉m, ngol hippugol gite gaayi e ndaarude faade e kon ko Alla harmini ﾉ砥rata laﾉ橡妬nnde on ka Alla. Pellet, Alla ko O Humpitiiﾉ熔 ko ﾉ兎 huuwata, hay e huunde e ﾉ蓉m suuﾉ預naaki Mo, aray O Yoﾉ殿 ﾉ兎 e dow ﾉ蓉m."
  24,31,"Maakan rewﾉ兎 gomﾉ擁nﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n yo ﾉ兎 hippu gite maﾉ橡兎 ﾉ容n gaayi ndaarude e ko daganaaki ﾉ兎 ndaarugol kon immorde e awraaji, ﾉ兎 reenira farjuuji maﾉ橡兎 ﾉ擁n woﾉ遼擁tagol pankare ﾉ容n e surrugol ﾉ擁, wata ﾉ兎 feﾃｱﾃｱinan cuﾉ預ari maﾉ橡兎 ndin jananﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n si wanaa ko feeﾃｱi kon e mayri, kon ko newotaako suuﾉ蓉gol ﾉ蓉m wano conci ﾉ擁n, yo ﾉ兎 fawu tiggaaje maﾉ橡兎 ﾉ容n e hoore jolﾉ容 wontirﾉ容 ﾉ容n ka senngo dow conci maﾉ橡兎 fii yo ﾉ兎 suuﾉ蓉 cukuli maﾉ橡兎 ﾉ擁n e geece maﾉ橡兎 ﾉ容n e daaﾉ容 maﾉ橡兎 ﾉ容n, wata ﾉ兎 feﾃｱﾃｱinan cuﾉ預ari maﾉ橡兎 suuﾉ擁indi ndin si wanaa moodiﾉ橡兎 maﾉ橡兎 ﾉ兎n, maaﾉ蓉m baabiraaﾉ兎 maﾉ橡兎 ﾉ兎n, maaﾉ蓉m baabiraaﾉ兎 moodiﾉ橡兎 maﾉ橡兎 ﾉ兎n, maaﾉ蓉m ﾉ妬ﾉ遼兎 maﾉ橡兎 ﾉ兎n, maaﾉ蓉m ﾉ妬ﾉ遼兎 moodiﾉ橡兎 maﾉ橡兎 ﾉ兎n, maaﾉ蓉m musiﾉ遼兎 maﾉ橡兎 ﾉ兎n, maaﾉ蓉m ﾉ妬ﾉ遼兎 musiﾉ遼兎 maﾉ橡兎 ﾉ兎n, maaﾉ蓉m ﾉ妬ﾉ遼兎 banndiraaﾉ兎 maﾉ橡兎 ﾉ兎n, maaﾉ蓉m sonnaaﾉ兎 maﾉ橡兎 hoolaaﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n, foti ko ﾉ兎 julﾉ兎 maa ko ﾉ兎 heeferﾉ兎, maaﾉ蓉m ﾉ兎n ﾉ兎 ﾉ兎 jeyi immorde e maccuﾉ兎 maaﾉ蓉m horﾉ兎, maaﾉ蓉m worﾉ兎 jokkooﾉ兎 ﾃｱiiri ﾉ兎 maraa haaju e rewﾉ兎, maaﾉ蓉m boobooﾉ兎 ﾉ兎 humpitaaki ﾉ兎n awraaji sonnaaﾉ兎 sabu famﾉ蓉gol maﾉ橡兎, wata sonnaaﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n fiyandir koyﾉ容 maﾉ橡兎 ﾉ容n faadagol fii yo annde ko ﾉ兎 suuﾉ擁 kon immorde e cuuﾉ預ari maﾉ橡兎 yeru liﾉ兎 e ko nanndi e ﾉ蓉m. Tuubee ruttoﾉ熔n ka Alla no fotuﾉ熔n fodde -ko onon yo gomﾉ擁nﾉ兎- tijjagol on heﾉ殿y ko ﾉ預ﾉ橡殿a kon, daﾉ熔n ko hulaa kon."
  24,32,"Resinee -onon gomﾉ擁nﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n- ﾉ兎n worﾉ兎 ﾉ兎 alah sonnaaﾉ兎, e ﾉ兎n rimﾉ兎 ﾉ兎 alaa moodiﾉ橡兎, resinee gomﾉ擁nﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n immorde e maccuﾉ兎 mooﾉ熔n ﾉ兎n e horﾉ兎 mooﾉ熔n ﾉ兎n kadi, si tawii ko ﾉ兎 waasuﾉ兎 Alla alﾉ擁niray ﾉ兎 ﾆ「ral Makko yaajungal ngal, Alla ko O Yaajuﾉ熔 Arsike, alﾉ擁nngol goﾉ遼熔 uytataa Arsike Makko on, ko O Annduﾉ熔 alhaaliiji jeyaaﾉ兎 Makko ﾉ兎n."
  24,33,"ﾆ‘n ﾉ兎 hattanaani resugol sabu baasal maﾉ橡兎, yo ﾉ兎 ﾉ預ﾉ橡砥 ﾉ砥urnaade gaa e jina ngon haa Alla alﾉ擁nira ﾉ兎 ﾆ「ral Makko Yaajungal ngal. ﾆ‘n maccuﾉ兎 wonuﾉ兎 ﾉ預ﾉ橡砥de soottaadede ka koohooﾉ兎 maﾉ橡兎 ﾉ兎n e dow yoﾉ砥gol jawdi fii yo ﾉ兎 rinﾉ蓉, no fawii koohooﾉ兎 maﾉ橡兎 ﾉ兎n jaﾉ殿nngol ﾉ兎 ﾉ蓉m, si ﾉ兎 anndirii ﾉ兎 hattaneede tottugol ngol e moﾆｴﾆｴugol ka diina, haray no fawii ﾉ兎 nde ﾉ兎 jonnata ﾉ兎 jawdi Alla ndi O jonni ﾉ兎 ndin, ﾉ蓉m woni ﾉ兎 fukkana ﾉ兎 peccun e ko ﾉ兎 winndi ﾉ兎 kon fii yoﾉ砥gol ﾉ蓉m. Wata on doolu horﾉ兎 mooﾉ熔n ﾉ兎n e jeeno fii ﾉ預ﾉ橡砥gol jawdi -wano Abdullaahi bun ubayyu waﾉ擁rnoo non horﾉ兎 makko ﾉ兎n ﾉ擁ﾉ熔 fewndo ﾉ兎 ﾉ預ﾉ橡砥noo nantagol e woﾉ遼擁tagol e pankare ﾉ容n- fii yo on ﾉ預ﾉ橡砥 ko o faggitori kon farju makko on, kala dooluﾉ熔 ﾉ兎 e mooﾉ熔n fii ﾉ蓉m, pellet, Alla ﾉ殿awo doolugol ﾉ兎 ngol ko O Surroowo junuubu maﾉ橡兎 on, Yurmeteeﾉ熔 ﾉ兎; sabu ko ﾉ兎 doolaaﾉ兎, bakkaatu on ko fawii ko e dooluﾉ熔 ﾉ兎 on."
  24,34,"Gomﾉ擁i Men tippinii e mooﾉ熔n -onon yimﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n- Aayeeje ﾉ殿nnguﾉ容 jilﾉ砥ya alah e majje, Men tippini e mooﾉ熔n misal immorde e ﾉ兎n feﾆｴﾆｴunooﾉ兎 ado mooﾉ熔n immorde e gomﾉ擁nﾉ兎 e heeferﾉ兎, Men tippini e mooﾉ熔n waaju ﾉ兎n hulooﾉ兎 Joomi mu'un hiﾉ兎 waajitora ngu ﾉ熔ftagol Yamraaﾉ擁 Makko ﾉ擁n e woﾉ遼擁tagol haﾉ預aﾉ擁 Makko ﾉ擁n."
  24,35,"Ko Alla woni ndaygu kammuuli ﾉ擁n e leydi ndin, e fewnoowo ﾉ兎n wonuﾉ兎 e majji. Sifa ndaygu Makko ngun ka ﾉ兎rnde gomﾉ擁nﾉ熔 on, ko wano tuﾉ遼容re e maadi ndaynginndi ndi alaa wuddere, hara pitilol no e mayri, pitilol ngol no e nder biiniiri fewtinaandi a wi'ayma ko ndi hoodere jalbunde. Ngol pitilol no huﾉ橡妬niree nebban leggal barkinaangal, ngal le ko leggal nebbantiwal ngal. Huunde heedah ngal leggal e naange ngen, wanaa ka bimmbi wanaa ka kiikiiﾉ容. Nebban maggal ﾉ預m no ﾉ預ﾉ殿 jalbude sabu laaﾉ砥gol majjam, hay si yiite meemaali ﾉ預m. Ko honno kan si yiite meemii ﾉ預m? Ndaygu pitilol ngol ﾉ兎ydoo e ndaygu biiniiri ndin. Ko nii de ﾉ兎rnde gomﾉ擁nﾉ熔 on wa'ata si ndaygu peewal ngal jalbii e mayre. Alla hino hawrinndina e jokkugol Alqur'aana on on mo O muuyi immorde e jeyaaﾉ兎 Makko ﾉ兎n. Alla no ﾉ殿nnginira piiji ﾉ擁n nanndo majji piyirgol ﾉ擁 mise. Alla ko Annduﾉ熔 kala huunde. Huunde suuﾉ預naaki Mo."
  24,36,"Ngol pitilol no huﾉ橡妬nee e nder Juulirﾉ容 ﾉ容 Alla Yamiri mahugol e townugol fii majje, Innde Makko jaﾅ逆oree e majje Noddinaandu ndun e Julde nden e jaﾅ逆agol ngol, no juulee e nder majje fii ﾉ預ﾉ橡砥gol welayee Alla ka arannde ﾃｱalal ngal e ka sakkitorde maggal."
  24,37,"Worﾉ兎 ﾉ兎 soodugol e yeeyugol maapintaa ﾉ蓉m gaayi jaﾅ逆agol Alla Senayee wonanii Mo, e tottirgol Julde nden no haaniri non, e jonnugol Jakka on henndotooﾉ兎 mo ﾉ兎n, hara hiﾉ兎 huli ﾃ疎lnde Darngal, nden ﾃ疎laande nde waylitoytoo e muuﾉ蓉m ﾉ兎rﾉ容 ﾉ容n hakkunde tama'u daﾉ蓉gol immorde e Lepte ﾉ容n e kulol majje, giiﾉ容 ﾉ容n waylitoyoo e mayre faade e nokku kala ka ﾉ容 yaari."
  24,38,"Ko ﾉ兎 golliri ﾉ蓉m ko fii yo Alla yoﾉ砥 ﾉ兎 e dow golle maﾉ橡兎 ﾉ容n ko ﾉ砥ri moﾆｴﾆｴude ko ﾉ兎 gollunoo kon, O ﾉ兎ydana ﾉ兎 kadi immorde e ﾆ「ral Makko ngal njoﾉ電i e dow mu'un. Alla no arsika on mo O Muuyi ko aldaa e hasboore e dow emmbere golle maﾉ橡兎 ﾉ容n, ko woni hiMo okka ﾉ兎 cowe ko ﾉ兎 gollunoo kon."
  24,39,"ﾆ‘n yedduﾉ兎 Alla, golle maﾉ橡兎 ﾉ容 ﾉ兎 golli ﾉ容n, ﾉ容 maraa baraaji, ko yeru merere wonnde e hollaande ﾉ熔nﾉ預aﾉ熔 on no yi'a nde o sikka ko nde ndiyam, o yaha e mayre haa si o hewtii o daroo e hoore mayre o heﾉ殿taa ndiyam, ko wano nii yedduﾉ熔 on himo sikka wonnde golle makko ﾉ容n ﾉ容 nafay mo, haa si o maayii o immintinaama hara o heﾉ殿tah baraaji golle ﾉ容n. O tawa Joomi makko yeeso makko O huuﾉ妬nana mo hasboore golle makko ﾉ容n haa timma, Alla ko O Yaawuﾉ熔 Hasboore."
  24,40,"Maaﾉ蓉m golle maﾉ橡兎 ﾉ容n ko yeru niﾉ兎 e nder maayo luggungo, no dow maggo benpeﾆｴﾆｴe, no dow ﾉ容n benpeﾆｴﾆｴe benpeﾆｴﾆｴe goo, no dow majje duule hiﾉ容 suddi koode tinddinorteeﾉ容 ﾉ容n, niﾉ兎 fawondirﾉ容 yoga e majje e dow yoga, si ukkiiﾉ熔 e ﾉ容e niﾉ兎 ﾉ熔o yaltinii junngo mu'un ngon o ﾉ殿dotaako yi'ugol ngo sabu saﾉ葉ude niﾉ兎 ﾉ容n, ko wano nii kadi yedduﾉ熔 on, gomﾉ擁i fawondirii e hoore makko niﾉ兎 majjere e sikke e wemmbere e uddeede ﾉ兎rnde makko, on mo Alla arsikaali Peewal immorde e majjere nden, e ganndal ka Deftere Makko, haray o marah peewal ngal o feewita ﾉ蓉m, wanah kadi deftere nde o ndaygirta ﾉ蓉m."
  24,41,"Kaa a anndaa -an Nulaaﾉ熔- wonndema Alla no subuhinanoo Mo ﾉ兎n wonuﾉ兎 ka kammuuli, no subuhinanoo Mo ﾉ兎n wonuﾉ兎 ka leydi immorde e tageefooji, colliﾉ擁n kadi no subuhinanoo Mo hiﾉ擁 fonti gabitanji(bibje) majji ka weeyo? Gootel kala e ﾉ擁i tageefooji Alla hiMo Annadi Julde kala juuluﾉ熔 immorde e majji wano neﾉ遼預nke on, e subuhinaali kala subuhiniiﾉ熔 immorde e majji wano colli ﾉ擁n, Alla ko O Annduﾉ熔 ko ﾉ兎 huuwata, suuﾉ預naaki Mo hay e huunde e golle maﾉ橡兎 ﾉ容n."
  24,42,"Ko Alla heeranii kanko tun Laamu kammuuli ﾉ擁n e Laamu leydi ndin, ko faade ka Makko Kanko tun woni ruttorde ﾃ疎lnde Darngal fii Hasboore e njoﾉ電i."
  24,43,"Kaa a anndaa -an Nulaaﾉ熔- wonndema Alla hiMo sogga duulere, refti O hawtindira yoga e cenkoy mayre faade e yoga, refti O waﾉ預 nde fawondirnde O dewta yoga e mayre e dow yoga, yi'aa toﾉ登 ngon no yalta ka nder duulere, no iwa ka kammu jippoo immorde e ﾉ容n duule sukkuﾉ容 nannduﾉ容 e pelle sabu mawnugol majje, [no yalta ton kadi] kunte ndiyam fenndiiﾉ預m wa'uﾉ預m wa koccuuje, O hewtina ﾉ容n marmalle on mo O Muuyi immorde jeyaaﾉ兎 Makko ﾉ兎n, O firta ﾉ容 e on mo O Muuyi e maﾉ橡兎, ndaygu maﾆｴe duule ﾉ容n no do'a naﾉ砥de giiﾉ容 ﾉ容n sabu saﾉ葉ude jalbugol majje."
  24,44,"Alla hiMo lontindira hakkunde jemma on e ﾃｱalorma on ka juutugol e ka raﾉ橡妬ﾉ蓉gol, e ka yahugol e ka arugol, pellet, no e ﾉ蓉m ko jaﾅ逆aa ﾉ熔o immorde e Aayeeje e daliilaaji joomayankooji waaju tinndinﾉ擁 e dow Kattanﾉ容 Alla e Ngootimmbaaku Makko wonannde joomoraaﾉ兎 giiﾉ容 ﾉ兎n."
  24,45,"Ko Alla Tagi kala ko woni ladude ka hoore leydi e mummunteeji ﾉ擁n immorde e toﾉ橡兎re [maniiyu], no e majji ﾉ擁n yaarooji reedu muuﾉ蓉m e daasagol wano mbolle ﾉ容n, no e majji ﾉ擁n yaarooji kayﾉ容 ﾉ擁ﾉ擁 wano neﾉ遼熔 on e sonndu ndun, no e majji kadi ﾉ擁n yaarooji [koyﾉ容] nayi wano neemoraaﾉ擁 ﾉ擁n, Alla hiMo Taga ko O Muuyi ko O jaﾅ逆ii kon e ko O jaﾅ逆aaki kon kadi, pellet, Alla ko O hattanﾉ熔 e dow kala huunde, hay e huunde ronkintah Mo."
  24,46,"Gomﾉ擁i Men Tellinii e dow Muhammadu (yo Alla juulu e makko hisna) Aayeeje ﾉ殿nnguﾉ容 ko jilﾉ妬 alah e majje, Alla hiMo hawrinndina on mo O Muuyi faade e Laawol focciingol, ngol ooﾃｱannde e muuﾉ蓉m, ngol Laawol yottina mo ka Aljanna."
  24,47,"Naafiqiiﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n no wi'a: ""Men gomﾉ擁nii Alla, men gomﾉ擁nii Nulaaﾉ熔 on, men ﾉ熔ftike Alla, men ﾉ熔ftike Nulaaﾉ熔 on kadi, refti fedde goo e maﾉ橡兎 huccita, hara ﾉ兎 ﾉ熔ftaaki Alla e Nulaaﾉ熔 Makko on ka yamaroore fii Jihaadi ka Laawol Alla e tanaa muuﾉ蓉m ﾉ殿awo ﾉ兎 aaﾆｴike ﾉ蓉m ko e gomﾉ擁nal Alla e Nulaaﾉ熔 Makko on e ﾉ熔ftagol ﾉ兎 kamﾉ兎 ﾉ擁ﾉ熔, ﾉ兎n huccituﾉ兎 gaayi ﾉ熔ftagol Alla e Nulaaﾉ熔 Makko on, ﾉ兎n wonaali gomﾉ擁nﾉ兎 hay si ﾉ兎 nodditike wonndema ko ﾉ兎 gomﾉ擁nﾉ兎."
  24,48,"Si ﾉ兎e naafiqiiﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n noddaama faade ka Alla, e ka Nulaaﾉ熔 on fii yo Nulaaﾉ熔 on ﾃｱaawu hakkunde maﾉ橡兎 fii koﾉ兎 wennjondiri e fii mu'un kon, tawa kamﾉ兎 ko ﾉ兎 ﾉ蓉urniiﾉ兎 gaayi ﾃｱaawoore makko nden sabu naafiqaaku maﾉ橡兎 ngun."
  24,49,"Si ﾉ兎 anndii hiﾉ兎 mari goonga, wonndema o ﾃｱaaway ko nafataﾉ兎, ﾉ兎 aray ka makko ko ﾉ兎 ﾉ熔ftiiﾉ兎 yankiniiﾉ兎."
  24,50,"Kaa hara wonu ka ﾉ兎rﾉ容 ﾉ兎e ﾃｱaw duumiingu e majje, kaa ﾉ兎 sikkiti wonnde kanko ko o Nulaaﾉ熔 Alla, kaa ﾉ兎 hulu wata Alla e Nulaaﾉ熔 Makko on tooﾃｱu ﾉ兎 ka ﾃｱaawoore? Hay e huunde e koo ko jaﾅ逆aaﾉ熔o wonaali, ko woni, ko sabu ﾃｱaw wonngu ka wonkiiji maﾉ橡兎 sabu ﾉ蓉uragol maﾉ橡兎 gaayi ﾃｱaawoore makko nden e sanndalingol nde."
  24,51,"Anndu ko wonata konngol gomﾉ擁nﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n si ﾉ兎 noddaama faade ka Alla e ka Nulaaﾉ熔 on fii yo ﾃｱaawu hakkunde maﾉ橡兎, ko nde ﾉ兎 wi'ata: ""Men nanii Daaluyee Makko on, men ﾉ熔ftike Yamiroore Makko nde."" ﾆ‘n siforﾉ兎 ﾉ擁i sifaaji ko kamﾉ兎 woni malaaﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n ka aduna e ka Laakara."
  24,52,"Kala ﾉ熔ftiiﾉ熔 Alla o ﾉ熔ftii Nulaaﾉ熔 Makko on, o jebbilanii ﾃｱaawoore Maﾉ橡兎 nden, o huli ko goopi ﾉ擁n pooﾉ預ta kon, o rentori e Lepte Alla ﾉ容n ﾉ熔ftagol Yamiroore Makko nden, e woﾉ遼擁tagol haﾉ預aﾉ擁 Makko ﾉ擁n, haray ﾉ兎n ﾉ熔n ko kamﾉ兎 tun woni maliraaﾉ兎 moﾆｴﾆｴere aduna on e Laakara on."
  24,53,"Naafiqiiﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n woondiri Alla kaddi goondooje maﾉ橡兎 tiiﾉ擁naaﾉ容 ﾉ容n ﾉ容ﾉ兎 hattani woondirgol ﾉ蓉m: ""Si a yamirii ﾉ兎 yaltugol yaha ka Jihaadi ma ﾉ兎 yaltu sanne"". Maakan ﾉ兎 -an Nulaaﾉ熔-: wata on woondu, penaale mooﾉ熔n ﾉ容n ko anndaaﾉ容, ﾉ熔ftaare mooﾉ熔n nde aaﾆｴiﾉ熔n nden ko anndaande. Alla ko O Humpitiiﾉ熔 ko golloton, hay e huunde e golle mo'on ﾉ容n suuﾉ預naaki Mo noone woo no suuﾉ擁rﾉ熔n ﾉ容."
  24,54,"An Nulaaﾉ熔 maakan ﾉ兎e naafiqiiﾉ兎: ﾆ覚ftee Alla ﾉ熔ftoﾉ熔n Nulaaﾉ熔 on, ka kene e ka gunndoo, si on huccitii gaayi e ko yamirﾉ熔n kon e ﾉ熔ftagol ﾉ兎 kamﾉ兎 ﾉ擁ﾉ熔; haray anndu ko fawii mo kanko, ko ko o fawaa kon immorde e yottinngol ngol, no fawii on onon kadi ko fawaﾉ熔n kon immorde e ﾉ熔ftagol ngol e gollirgol ko O addi kon, si on ﾉ熔ftorii mo gollugol ko o yamiri on kon gollugol e accugol ko o haﾉ擁 on kon, on feeway faande e goonga kan, fawaaki Nulaaﾉ熔 on si wanaa yottinngol ﾉ殿nngungol, fawaaki mo fawugol on e dow peewal ngal, e doolugol on e dow maggal."
  24,55,"Alla Fodii ﾉ兎n gomﾉ擁nﾉ兎 Mo jeyaaﾉ兎 e mooﾉ熔n ﾉ兎 golli golle moﾆｴﾆｴe ﾉ容n, nde O wallata ﾉ兎 e dow ayﾉ兎 maﾉ橡兎 ﾉ兎n, o waﾉ預 ﾉ兎 lontiiﾉ兎 ka leydi yeru no O waﾉ擁ranoo non ﾉ兎n gomﾉ擁nﾉ兎 adiiﾉ兎 ﾉ兎 lontiiﾉ兎 e mayri, O Fodi ﾉ兎 nde O waﾉ預ta diina maﾉ橡兎 ka O weltorani ﾉ兎 kan -ﾉ蓉m le ko Diina Lislaamu kan- weeﾉ砥ka Tedduka, O fodi ﾉ兎 O wattitanay ﾉ兎 ﾉ殿awo kulol maﾉ橡兎 ngol hoolaare. Yo ﾉ兎 rewam Min tun, wata ﾉ兎 sirkanam hay e huunde. Kala yedduﾉ熔 ﾉ殿awo on neema hara ﾉ兎n ﾉ熔n ko kamﾉ兎 woni yaltuﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n gaayi ﾉ熔ftaare Alla."
  24,56,"Tottiree Julde nden no haaniri non, jonnon Jakka jawle mooﾉ熔n ﾉ容n, ﾉ熔ftoron kadi Nulaaﾉ熔 on gollugol ko o yamiri on kon e accugol ko o haﾉ擁 on kon e muuﾉ蓉m, jortagol on heﾉ殿y Yurmeende Alla nden."
  24,57,"Wata a sikku -an Nulaaﾉ熔- ﾉ兎n yedduﾉ兎 Alla ﾉ兎 laawoto Lam si Mi faalaama jippingol Lepte ﾉ容n e maﾉ橡兎, jaaﾆｴorde maﾉ橡兎 nden ﾃ疎lnde Darngal ko Jahannama. On mo Jahannama woni wattinirde mu'un pellet, haray wattabde makko nden bonii."
  24,58,"Ko onon yo gomﾉ擁nﾉ兎 Alla, ﾉ兎 golliri Sari'a mo O waﾉ預ni ﾉ兎 on, yo ﾉ預ﾉ橡砥 duﾅ蟻yee e mooﾉ熔n maccuﾉ兎 mooﾉ熔n ﾉ兎n e horﾉ兎 mooﾉ熔n ﾉ兎n e sukaaﾉ兎 mooﾉ熔n rimﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n, ﾉ兎n ﾉ兎 yottaaki duuﾉ妬 kellefuyee e waqtuuji tati: Ko adii Julde Subaka nden, waqtu wattitugol conci waalorﾉ擁 ﾉ擁n e conci gollirﾉ擁 ﾉ擁n, e ka waqtu jolloro tuma ﾉ登rtoto ﾉ熔n conci mooﾉ熔n fii ﾉ熔ykal njolloor, e ka ﾉ殿awo Julde geeﾆｴe; sabu ko on fewndo ﾉ登rtotoﾉ熔n conci mooﾉ熔n gollirﾉ擁 ﾉ擁n ﾉ登rnoﾉ熔n conci ﾉ預anorﾉ擁 ﾉ擁n, ﾉ擁i waqtuuji ﾉ熔o tati ko awraaji mooﾉ熔n, wata ﾉ兎 naatu ka mooﾉ熔n e majji si wonaa ﾉ殿awo duﾅ蟻yee mooﾉ熔n. Bakkaatu fawaaki on fii naatugol maﾉ橡兎 hara ﾉ兎 cakkitinaaki, bakkaatu fawaaki ﾉ兎 ko wonaa e nder ﾉ擁iﾉ熔o immorde e waqtuuji. kamﾉ兎 ko ﾉ兎 heewuﾉ兎 wangagol, yoga e mooﾉ熔n kadi no liigoo ka yoga, gasataa haﾉ蓉gol ﾉ兎 naatugol e kala waqtu si wanaa ﾉ兎 duﾅ喫ni. Ko wano Alla ﾉ殿nnginirani on nii ﾃｱaawooje duﾅ喫nagol ngol O ﾉ殿nnginiranta on Aayeeje tinndinﾉ容 e ko O Sar'inani on kon immorde e ﾃｱaawooje. Alla ko Annduﾉ熔 nafaaji jeyaaﾉ兎 Makko ﾉ兎n ko O ﾃ粗eﾃｱuﾉ熔 e nder waﾉ預nngol ﾉ兎 ngol ﾃｱaawooje."
  24,59,"Si sukaaﾉ兎 mooﾉ熔n yottike duuﾉ妬 kellefuyoo, yo ﾉ兎 ﾉ預ﾉ橡砥 yamiroore tuma naatugol ka cuuﾉ擁 e waqtuuji ﾉ擁n fow, yeru ko jaﾅ逆aa kon e fiyaake mawﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n ko adii, wano Alla ﾉ殿nnginirani on nii ﾃｱaawooje duﾅ喫nagol ngol Alla ﾉ殿nnginiranta on Aayeeje Makko ﾉ容n, Alla ko O Annduﾉ熔 nafaaji jeyaaﾉ兎 Makko ﾉ兎n, ﾃ粗eﾃｱuﾉ熔 e ko O Sar'inani ﾉ兎 kon."
  24,60,"E ﾉ兎n yummiraaﾉ兎 accuﾉ兎 fiilaade e sowaade sabu nayewu maﾉ橡兎, ﾉ兎n ﾉ兎 tamﾆｴinaaki e dewgal bakkaatu fawaaki ﾉ兎 si ﾉ兎 wallinii conci maﾉ橡兎 ﾉ擁n wano waanaare nden e tiggaare nden, hara ﾉ兎 feﾃｱﾃｱinaali cuﾉ預ari suuﾉ擁inde ndin, ndi Alla yamiri ndin suuﾉ蓉gol. Ko nde ﾉ兎 accata wallinngol ﾉ擁n conci ﾉ砥ri moﾆｴﾆｴannde ﾉ兎 diini wallinngol ﾉ擁, ka tentinngol fii surragol e nantagol, Alla ko O Nanoowo konnguﾉ擁 mooﾉ熔n ﾉ擁n, Annduﾉ熔 golle mooﾉ熔n ﾉ容n, hay huunde e ﾉ蓉m suuﾉ預naaki Mo, aray O yoﾉ殿 on e dow majje."
  24,61,"Junuubu fawaaki on bunﾉ熔 waasaaﾉ熔 giiﾉ容 mu'un; junuubu fawaaki kadi laﾆｴuﾉ熔 on, junuubu fawaaki kadi nawnuﾉ熔 on; si ﾉ兎 ﾉ預lii ko ﾉ兎 hattantaake kon daranagol ﾉ蓉m immorde e ko fawii ﾉ兎 waﾉ蓉gol wano Jihaadi ka Laawol Alla. Junuubu fawaaki on -onon gomﾉ擁nﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n- fii ﾃｱaamugol ka cuuﾉ擁 mooﾉ熔n, no jeyaa e majji cuuﾉ擁 ﾉ妬ﾉ遼兎 mooaon, wanaa kadi fii ﾃｱaamugol ka cuuﾉ擁 baabiraaﾉ兎 mooﾉ熔n, maaﾉ蓉m neeniraaﾉ兎 mooﾉ熔n, maaﾉ蓉n musiﾉ遼兎 mooﾉ熔n, maaﾉ蓉m musiﾉ遼兎 mooﾉ熔n rewﾉ兎, maaﾉ蓉m bappiraaﾉ兎 mooﾉ熔n, maaﾉ蓉m yaayiraaﾉ兎 mooﾉ熔n, maaﾉ蓉m kawiraaﾉ兎 mooﾉ熔n, maaﾉ蓉m neeniraaﾉ兎 mooﾉ熔n ka dewol, maaﾉ蓉m cuuﾉ擁 ﾉ擁 halfinaﾉ熔n reenugol ﾉ擁n wano aynuﾉ熔 awru. Junuuﾉ砥 alaa e ﾃｱaamugol ka cuuﾉ擁 yiﾉ遼兎 mooﾉ熔n sabu weleede wonkii makko e ﾉ蓉m, junuubu fawaaki on nde ﾃｱaamoton ko on mooﾉ妬iﾉ兎 maaﾉ蓉m ﾃｱaamiron gooto-gooto. Si on natay e cuuﾉ擁 sifa ﾉ擁i cuuﾉ擁 jaﾅ逆aaﾉ擁 ﾉ熔o e tanaa majji haray salminee ﾉ兎n wonuﾉ兎 e nder majji ﾉ蓉m woni wi'on: ""Kisiyee e mon"" Si tawii goﾉ遼熔 alah e nder majji; haray salminee e dow wonkiiji mooﾉ熔n, ﾉ蓉m woni wi'on: ""Kisiyee e amen e jeyaaﾉ兎 Alla moﾆｴﾆｴuﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n"". ﾆ隔m ko hiwraango immorde ka Alla ngo O Sar'inani on barkinaango; sabu ko ngo saakata kon immorde e giggol e woowoniral hakkunde mooﾉ熔n, laaﾉ砥ngo no laaﾉ妬ra sabu maggo wonkii nanuﾉ熔 ngo on, ko yeru ngol ﾉ殿nnginngol aditiingol ka Simoore Alla ﾉ殿nnginirta Aayeeje jortagol on hakkilanay ﾉ容, gollitiron ko woni kon e nder majje."
  24,62,"Anndu gomﾉ擁nﾉ兎 goonguﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n ka gomﾉ擁nal maﾉ橡兎, ko ﾉ兎n woni gomﾉ擁nﾉ兎 Alla ﾉ兎 gomﾉ擁ni kadi Nulaaﾉ熔 Makko on, si ﾉ兎 laatike hiﾉ兎 wondi e Annabiijo on (yo Alla juulu e makko hisna) e fiyaake hawtinirﾉ熔 ﾉ兎 fii nafa Julﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n, ﾉ兎 yahatah haa ﾉ兎 ﾉ預ﾉ橡妬ra mo duﾅ蟻yee fii yahugol. Pellet, ﾉ兎n ﾉ預ﾉ橡妬rooﾉ兎 ma -an Nulaaﾉ熔- duﾅ蟻yee tuma yahugol ko ﾉ兎n ﾉ熔n gomﾉ擁ni Alla, ﾉ兎 gomﾉ擁ni Nulaaﾉ熔 Makko on e goonga, si ﾉ兎 ﾉ預ﾉ橡妬rii ma duﾅ蟻yee fii yoga e fiyaake hittuﾉ熔 e maﾉ橡兎 duﾅ蟻no on mo yiﾉ蓉ﾉ預a duﾅ蟻naade e maﾉ橡兎, ﾉ預ﾉ橡殿naaﾉ兎 yawtaneede junubaaji ﾉ擁n. Pellet, Alla ko O Yawtoowo tububaaji kala tuubuﾉ熔 immorde jeyaaﾉ兎 makko ﾉ兎n, ko O Yurmeteeﾉ熔 ﾉ兎."
  24,63,"Teddinee -onon gomﾉ擁nﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n- Nulaaﾉ熔 Alla on, si on nodday mo, wata on noddir mo innde makko nden, yeru: ""Ko an Muhammadu"" maaﾉ蓉m innde baaba makko nden, yeru: ""Ko an yo geﾉ預l Abdullahi"" Wano yoga e mooﾉ熔n waﾉ擁rta non e yoga, kono wi'ee: ""Ko an yo Nulaaﾉ熔 Alla, ko an yo Annabaajo Alla"" Si o noddii on kadi e muraadu kafaandu(renndaandu) wata on waﾉ蓉 noddaandu makko ndun wano noddaandu yoga e mooﾉ熔n e yoga e muuraaﾉ擁 puyﾉ擁, ko woni, yaccinee nootagol ndu. Gomﾉ擁i Alla no Anndi ﾉ兎n suuﾉ熔tooﾉ兎 yaha hara waynaaki, ﾉ兎n wonuﾉ兎 lunndaade yamaruyee Nulaaﾉ熔 on yo ﾉ兎 rento wata Alla hewtin ﾉ兎 jarrabuyeeji e masiibooji, maaﾉ蓉m O hewtina ﾉ兎 Lepte muusuﾉ容 ﾉ容 ﾉ兎 muﾃｱﾃｱotaako e hoore mu'un."
  24,64,"Ko non woniri, pellet, ko Alla tun woodani tagude e jeyde e fewjude ko woni kon ka kammuuli e ka leydi, hiMo Anndi -onon yimﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n- ko wonuﾉ熔n kon e mu'un immorde e alhaaliiji, hay huunde e majji suuﾉ預naaki Mo, ﾃ疎lnde Darngal -tuma ﾉ兎 ruttiroytee ka Makko Immital ﾉ殿awo maayde nden- O humpita ﾉ兎 ko ﾉ兎 gollunoo kon immorde e golle ka aduna, Alla ko O Annduﾉ熔 kala huunde, hay e huunde suuﾉ預naaki Mo ka kammuuli wanaa ka leydi kadi."
